 rvices (PeerTube\, Mastodon\, Owncast\, Lemmy)\, email\, VPN\, private clo
 ud storage\, wikis and more. Project results released under open source li
 cences. Deadline 1 June 2026\, 12:00 CEST.\n\nOrganisation: NLnet / NGI Fe
